Please make sure that domain was unlocked with current registrar end before submitting transfer request. You can check and confirm it from whois. Just run command **whois domain.com**

Now customer can transfer their domain names to our registrar using new new client portal 

Here is the steps.
 

    Go to serverpointapps.com >> log in to Client Portal.
    Go to Menu >> Domain Names.
    Click on button  New domain / transfer.
    Click on Registrar Transfer under Register or transfer a new domain.
    Fill up the transfer form with necessary details and submit the form.
